text: Suonenjoki is a city in Northern Savonia, Finland. It had almost 7,500 living there in January 2014. The municipalities next to it are Kuopio, Leppävirta, Pieksämäki, Rautalampi and Tervo. == Other websites == * Suonenjoki site Category:Cities in Finland Category:Municipalities of North Savo
